org.elasticsearch.websocket.http.netty.client

Class NettyWebSocketClientHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jboss.netty.channel.SimpleChannelUpstreamHandler
      • org.elasticsearch.websocket.http.netty.client.NettyWebSocketClientHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WebSocketClient, org.jboss.netty.channel.ChannelHandler, org.jboss.netty.channel.ChannelUpstreamHandler

    public class NettyWebSocketClientHandler
extends org.jboss.netty.channel.SimpleChannelUpstreamHandler
implements WebSocketClient
    Handles socket communication for a connected WebSocket client. Not intended for end-users. Please use NettyWebSocketClient or NettyWebSocketActionListener for controlling your client.
    Author:
    Carl Byström
